text: Dania Popescu (born 11 June 1956) is a Romanian equestrian. She competed in the team jumping event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Romania Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
